jcuda.jcudpp
Class CUDPPOperator

java.lang.Object
  jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPOperator

public class CUDPPOperator
extends java.lang.Object

Operators supported by CUDPP algorithms (currently scan and segmented scan).

These are all binary associative operators.

See Also:
CUDPPConfiguration, JCudpp.cudppPlan(jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPHandle, jcuda.jcudpp.CUDPPConfiguration, long, long, long)
